                            HTML NES ASM
                              by Mibi88

A small JS assembler for the NES that I quickly wrote to code NES games on my
phone without needing Termux so the code is atrocious.

It currently generates NROM 128 roms.

    USAGE

Open index.html or index_base64.html if index.html is not working properly.

